# Cognote Roadmap

Purpose: concise, standardized product roadmap based on completed work from `CHANGELOG.md`, with a format that can be extended for future tasks.

## Standard Format
Use this format for all new roadmap entries:

```
## [Task X.Y] - YYYY-MM-DD
Status: Completed | In Progress | Planned
Area: Foundation | Audio | Transcription | Pipeline | Learning | Library | UX | Performance | Distribution
Summary: 1-2 sentence feature summary.
Delivered:
- Capability 1
- Capability 2
- Capability 3
```

